snippet.title: Life in the Vale - Dragonvale Gameplay
snippet.description:
Subscribe: https://goo.gl/pWXxhP 

Please leave a Like. It would be a BIG help! Thanks!

Hello Valers!
We're back in the park Breeding Dragons, setting Quests, collecting Gems, grabbing lots of Dragon Cash and going to the Dragon Races!

Follow along with me daily in Dragonvale, breeding new Dragons, sharing cool tips and growing my park. Sort of like a vlog or in this case a Glog (Game Log)!

Let me know what you would like to see for upcoming videos in the comments.

You can add me for coop breeding!
Game Center - gdavis335

Time For Some Fun WebSite: http://www.timeforsomefun.com
